</li>
<li id="cite_note-23"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-23">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Rehurek, R., A combined system for vector similarity search based on the inverted fulltext index, <a href="/w/index.php?title=ScaleText_Search_Engine&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="ScaleText Search Engine (page does not exist)">ScaleText Search Engine</a>, Pending U.S. Patent 15726803, 2017.</span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-24"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-24">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Croft, B., Metzler, D., Strohman, T., Search Engines, Information Retrieval in Practice, Addison Wesley, 2009.</span>
</li>
</ol></div>
